FROM ubuntu:22.04

WORKDIR /src

RUN apt-get update && \

    build-essential \
    calibre \
    pandoc \

    ruby \

    xvfb \
    zlib1g-dev \
    && gem install bundler \
    && bundle install \
    && apt-get remove -y --purge build-essential \
    && apt-get clean

COPY . /src

ENTRYPOINT ["/src/bootstrap.sh"]

VOLUME ["/output"]
